quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ana tunkulupilile mmwe kutendaga ŵaakunkuya ni ŵandu ŵapasi?”"
  26,112,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana umanyilisichi ungwete pa yaŵaliji nkutenda ŵanganyao?”"
  26,113,"“Nganichiŵatu chiŵalanjilo chao ikaŵeje kwa Ambuje ŵangu, ingaŵe mwamanyililaga.”"
  26,114,“Soni nganimba une jwanti ni kwaŵinga ŵakulupilila.”
  26,115,“Nganimba une ikaŵeje nkutetela jwakuonechela.”
  26,116,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Naga ngankuleka E mmwe Nuhu! Chisimu chene chim’be mwa akusomedwa maganga.”"
  26,117,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu ŵandu ŵangu angaaniile.”"
  26,118,"“Basi jilanyani chilikati changune ni ŵanganyao ni chilanyo (chambone), ni munjokole une ni ŵandu ŵali none mu ŵakulupilila.”"
  26,119,Basi ni twan’jokwele jwalakwe pamo ni ŵaŵaliji najo m’chombo chepachile
  26,120,Kaneko ni twamisisye ŵakusigalao panyuma pakwe
  26,121,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,122,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,123,Achina Adi ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,124,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Hudu kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,125,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,126,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,127,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵatu malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,128,“Ana nkutaŵa pachikwesya palipose pakusalala nyumba syeleuleu mwamasanje (pagamba kusaka kulosya machili ngaŵa syagonamo)?”
  26,129,“Ni nkulitaŵila makome gamakulungwakulungwa nti chisawu tinnonjele?”
  26,130,“Soni ntite mpute ngondo nkasaputa mwakulikwesya.”
  26,131,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,132,“Soni mun’jogopani Ajula jwampele ichindu (yambonembone) yankuimanyilila.”
  26,133,“Ampele ilango ni ŵanache.”
  26,134,“Kwisa soni migunda ni sulo syatutumule.”
  26,135,“Chisimu une ngun’jogopela ŵanganyammwe ilagasyo ya lisiku lyekulungwa.”
  26,136,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Yalumope kukwetu, n’jamuche kapena nkaŵa mwa akwamuka.”"
  26,137,“Nganiyiŵatu ayi (yatukutendayi) ikaŵeje nyendele ja ŵandu ŵandanda.”
  26,138,“Soni nganituŵatu uwwe ŵanti ni kupedwa ilagasyo.”
  26,139,"Basi ŵankaaniile, ni twajonasile. Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,140,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,141,Achina Samuda ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,142,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Swaleh kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,143,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,144,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,145,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵa malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,146,“Ana (nkuganichisya kuti) tin’gambe kulechedwa mwantunjelele pa yaili pepanoyi.”
  26,147,"“M’migunda ni sulo syatutumule,”"
  26,148,“Ni mmela kwisa soni mitende itungatunga yakwe yakutependala?”
  26,149,“Soni nkusepa m’matumbi majumba mwa ufundi.”
  26,150,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,151,“Ni ngasimpikanila chilamusi cha akupunda malile (pasambi).”
  26,152,"“Aŵala ŵaakuwatanganya pa chilambo, soni ŵangajilanya.”"
  26,153,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Chisimu mmwe n’di mwa akulojedwa.”"
  26,154,"“Nganim’ba mmwe ikaŵeje mundu mpela uwwewe, basi ikani nacho chisimosimo naga n’di mwa akuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  26,155,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Aji ngamiya jajikongwe; jikwete kumwa (mesi), nombe jenumanja nkwete kumwa (mesi) palisiku lyakumanyika (ngamiya lisiku lyakwe nombe jenumanja lisiku lyenu).”"
  26,156,“Ni ngasin’jikwaya ni yakusakala iliyose itakwisa mwainkwembekenye ilagasyo yalisiku lyekulungwa.”
  26,157,"Nambo ŵanganyao ŵajisikite, mwanti ŵasyuchile kuŵa ŵakuligamba"
  26,158,"Basi ni yakwembekenye ilagasyo. Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,159,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,160,Ŵandu ŵa Lutwi ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,161,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Lutwi kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,162,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,163,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,164,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵa malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,165,"“Ana nkwaichilila achalume (achimijenu pakwatenda matanyula) mu iwumbe,”"
  26,166,“Ni nkwaleka aŵala ŵan’guumbiile Ambuje ŵenu kuti aŵeje achiŵammakwenu? Nambo jenumanja ni ŵandu ŵakusumba mpika.”
  26,167,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Naga ngankuleka (yakutukanya matanyula) mmwe Lutwi! Chisimu chene chim’be mwa akukoposyedwa.”"
  26,168,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Chisimu une ni jumpepe mwa akuiŵenga mwaukali itendo yenu (yamatanyulai).”"
  26,169,“Ambuje ŵangu! Munjokolani une ni liŵasa lyangu ku yaakupanganya ŵanganyaŵa.”
  26,170,Ni twan’jokwele jwalakwe ni liŵasa lyakwe lyosopelyene
  26,171,Ikaŵeje kangalamba kachikongwe (ŵankwao Lutwi ŵaŵaliji) mwa akusigalila munyuma
  26,172,Kaneko ni twajonasile ŵaneo
  26,173,Ni twagwichisye ŵanganyao wula (jamaganga). Kaje kusakala wula ja akuteteledwa
  26,174,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,175,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,176,Achinsyene itekete (ŵandu ŵa ku Madiyana) ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,177,"Ndema jaŵasalile Shuaibu kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,178,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,179,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,180,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵa malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"